The following components were ported from Kotlin/Java to Go with modifications:
- ComparisonPolicy, ComparisonUtil, TrimUtil
- DiffIterable, FairDiffIterable, and related iterable implementations
- DiffFragment, LineFragment, and related fragment types
- Range, LineOffsets, Enumerator
- ByLineRt (line-level diff), ByWordRt (word-level diff), ByCharRt (char-level diff)
- Myers LCS algorithm and related utilities

